{"tid":940982,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"孖辮墮胎雞出150蚊寫真","createTime":"2018-12-14T11:22:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T21:42:34.000Z","uid":21832,"like":25,"dislike":281,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"fee6d4fde0510fb840892d71ee62996e9ec023f5","tid":940982,"uid":21832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T11:22:25.000Z","msg":"18歲臭雞上年去深圳墮胎<br />\n個bb仲要唔係佢男朋友嘅（一男一女自拍張圖係佢同bb老竇 男嘅唔負責最後搞到要隻雞嘅男朋友埋單）<br />\n拍拖期間多次瞞著男朋友同影師上房影相<br />\n拍兩次拖最後都比人飛咗<br />\n仲成日問前度攞錢<br />\n落仔前喊到梨花帶雨話驚痛<br />\n最後話：好撚開心個肚少咗個賤種（我想講個bb係無辜）<br />\n而家出嚟賣貞節牌坊出「學妹系列 / 小狼系列寫真」<br />\n真係一朵白蓮花<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zi67xoX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fzi67xoX.jpg&h=31fbf8f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MmZgzH5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMmZgzH5.jpg&h=c3340a83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/i2lZyIj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fi2lZyIj.jpg&h=51a6c4d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5Ueb1X1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5Ueb1X1.jpg&h=1e422c59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/O3mRLT8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FO3mRLT8.jpg&h=5ca69bf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cBeYdtk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FcBeYdtk.jpg&h=fcaa131d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pCldVzM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FpCldVzM.jpg&h=de650de3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bjcKUPa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FbjcKUPa.jpg&h=58939478&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0oXqYsS.jpg\" data-t